name: doylesee.github.io
body:
Hi! My name is Doyle. I do front-end web development and have worked with the IT industry since 2006, helping build amazing softwares and countless websites. I also do graphic designs on my free time and run Killa, a brand which I started late 2009.

I have a solo music project under the alias, Johnny62 and play guitars for Guilttoflow as well as session for several other local bands in my area.

Where I'm @:
[doyleinigosee@gmail.com](mailto:doyleinigosee@gmail.com)

Where I'm really at:
Burnaby, BC CA
